The date is already `yyyyMMdd` in most paths, but the debugger earlier showed the historical date arriving as `"20260430 "` (trailing space), and after the refactor the date flows through `RequestDatesContext`. Normalize it explicitly so the value written to the `Date` column is guaranteed `YYYYMMDD`.

